                <head>National (?) Democracy</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt>"The South may despise them, refuse to associate with them, and even spit
                    in their faces, and yet they will crawl after them like whining spaniels and beg
                    to be permitted to gather up the crumbs that fall from the tables of their
                    masters."</excerpt>
