                <summary>Article takes great pleasure in recalling Democrats' 1856 claims to have
                    fielded the nation's only national party. Now they are the sectional party
                    themselves, it insists. It especially takes Northern Democrats to task for their
                    cowering subservience to the "lords-of-the-lash."</summary>
                <note/>
